metadata.name: Queen TARA /  The Golden Age
metadata.description:
The cosmic energy alignements assisted in bringing forward what we need to shed, release, and re evaluate. All to illuminate the no longer needed hand me downs of limiting beliefs passed by generation like DNA.
All the prepare us for " the golden age of transformation" to awaken to who we are at this time. As the waves upon us re-birth the promised energy of the Divine Feminine. The loving energy flow of balance, creation, intuition, and the spiritual-heart of the feminine.
